---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy â€” Threadmark"
  description="How Threadmark handles your data."
>
  <section class="privacy container">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="updated">Last updated: February 2026</p>

    <h2>What we collect</h2>
    <p>
      When you submit a form on this site, we collect your email address and any
      additional information you provide (such as your name or company). This
      data is stored by Netlify as our form submission provider.
    </p>

    <h2>How we use it</h2>
    <p>
      We use the information you submit solely to contact you about Threadmark,
      including product updates and launch announcements. We do not sell, share,
      or distribute your information to third parties.
    </p>

    <h2>Data storage</h2>
    <p>
      Form submissions are stored securely by Netlify. For details on how
      Netlify handles data, see
      <a
        href="https://www.netlify.com/privacy/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">Netlify's privacy policy</a
      >.
    </p>

    <h2>Your rights</h2>
    <p>
      You can request access to, correction of, or deletion of your data at any
      time by emailing us at
      <a href="mailto:privacy@threadmark.com">privacy@threadmark.com</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      If you have questions about this policy, email
      <a href="mailto:privacy@threadmark.com">privacy@threadmark.com</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .privacy {
    padding: 3rem 0;
    max-width: 40rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .updated {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  p {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }

  a {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  a:hover {
    text-decoration: none;
  }
</style>
